    <title type="html"><![CDATA[程序员的《权利法案》]]></title>
    <link href="http://blog.forecho.com/cheng-xu-yuan-de-quan-li-fa-an.html"/>
    <updated>2013-11-02T12:38:00+00:00</updated>
